'''''Reliance''''' has been the name of four known [[Starship/Legends|starships]] throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] history:
*'''''[[Reliance I]]''''', a [[Republic command ship]] used against the [[Krath/Legends|Krath]]
*'''''[[Reliance (Mandalorian Wars)|Reliance]]''''', a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] [[Flagship/Legends|flagship]] in the [[Mandalorian Wars]]
*'''''[[Reliance (Star Destroyer)|Reliance]]''''', a [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]]
*'''''[[Reliance (star hauler)|Reliance]]''''', an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Modular taskforce cruiser|Star Hauler]]
